description: An illustrative cartoon sticker depicts a distraught nun with a fair complexion, blonde bobbed hair, and striking red lipstick. She wears a traditional nun's habit, rendered in shades of white and purple. A wooden cross hangs from a thin chain around her neck. Her expression is one of exasperation or disappointment, as her eyes are closed and her left hand is held up to her forehead in a facepalm gesture.
